question: [提问方式1]Omada Central Essentials Parameters

answer: Description | A unified free cloud platform for networking and surveillance, offering lifetime free cloud management without additional fees, on-premises controllers, or VMS :contentReference[oaicite:1]{index=1}
Setup & Provisioning | Super-easy setup with automatic device identification and Zero-Touch Provisioning (ZTP) :contentReference[oaicite:2]{index=2}
Access & Management | Manage and monitor anytime via app or web; unlimited management scale for multiple sites :contentReference[oaicite:3]{index=3}
Supported Devices | Comprehensive portfolio including gateways, switches, APs, cameras, NVRs, and solar power systems :contentReference[oaicite:4]{index=4}
Surveillance Features | Easy-to-use networking for surveillance, including remote camera reboot; free video monitoring with third-party camera management, cross-site live view, and precise event management :contentReference[oaicite:5]{index=5}
Maintenance Tools | Provides topology, site map, troubleshooting tools, backup/reboot/upgrade schedules, and auto-maintenance rules for efficient upkeep :contentReference[oaicite:6]{index=6}
