question: [提问方式1]Omada Central Parameters

answer: Unified Cloud Management | Centrally manage Omada access points, switches, gateways, VIGI cameras, NVRs, and solar power systems via app or web (Essentials: free; Standard: license-based) :contentReference[oaicite:1]{index=1}
Easy Deployment & Setup | Automatic device detection, one-click adoption, Zero-Touch Provisioning (ZTP), automatic topology recognition, one-click Extend Mode and QoS :contentReference[oaicite:2]{index=2}
Remote Maintenance & Troubleshooting | Unified system for topology view, remote camera reboot, camera offline alerts, cable testing, and integrated troubleshooting tools :contentReference[oaicite:3]{index=3}
AI-Powered Video Monitoring | Cross-site live view, precise event management, people/vehicle analytics, accurate people counting, multi-store customer flow monitoring :contentReference[oaicite:4]{index=4}
Fully Cloud-Based | No need for on-premises hardware controllers or VMS; simplifies management and scaling :contentReference[oaicite:5]{index=5}
Versions & Scalability | Essentials: free, simplified for small businesses; Standard: paid license unlocking advanced features; scalable multi-site management :contentReference[oaicite:6]{index=6}
